UID and USER
--------------------
 - it will return the UID and name of the user
 - From current user andn id of that user

	++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 		 
	SQL> select user,uid from dual;

	USER
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	       UID
	----------
	SYSTEM
	         9


	SQL> 
